Title: Mistie's Mix Magic
Description:
The kith of Loamm request the skills of an alchemist! We have heard tales of the wondrous concoctions you uplanders have devised!

We have alchemists of our own down below! Miss Mistie has requested a few of these items.

Make a delivery to Loamm as soon as you can, won't you?
ObjectivesText: Deliver Aerated Mana Potions and Omnium Draconis to Mistie in Loamm.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Deliver the items to Mistie in Loamm
